      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lighter</strong> <strong>asparagus & pea</strong> <strong>speltotto</strong> topped with the <strong>basil drizzle</strong> and<strong> cheesy asparagus tips</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped basil </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
